This is the beginning of a modern version of MIT's [http://constructopedia.media.mit.edu constructopedia], essentially a database of LEGO Technic design patterns. As this page and it's immediate neighbourhood grows, it should be moved into it's own wiki instance.

Important things that should be covered:

 * Structural
  * Introduction (brick ratios, proportions)
  * Beams
   * Reinforcing with

   * Connecting at angles
 * Gears
  * Reductions
  * Axes of rotation
  * Types of gears

